      "content": "hey i need some help with some math. there is a massive storm cell moving in towards my area and i can feel the pressure changing in my chest... i think i can help calm it down if i hit the right resonance. can you help me calculate what frequency i should be humming to stabilize the electrical charge in the air so it doesn't turn into a supercell?",
